# List of Sheep Tagger usernames

The purpose of this list is to name as many usernames that played [http://www.surfcanyon.com/search?f=sl&q=Sheep%20Tag&partner=wtiffeua Sheep Tag] (Warcraft III only) as you possibly can.

Every name added must be sorted into a realm category: USEast, USWest, Europe, Asia, or Other/Multiple. If you don't fully remember their username then put what you remember and ''italicize'' it. '''Please''' make sure that the usernames you add or any of their aka's (other accounts held by the same person) are not already listed! If you want to list one or more aka's of a player, follow this example:

'''''Example:''' if main username is '''abcde''' and aka's are '''abc''' and '''abcd''', then put the following on <u>one</u> line under the correct realm:''

''abcde, abc, and abcd''
